intervention.description:
Juvederm Volbella: 15mg/ml, it is injected 1.5ml per patient per treatment (a total of 3ml per patient split in 2 treatment sessions at a 4 months interval);
Juvederm Volifit: 17.5mg/ml, it is injected 3ml per patient per treatment (a total of 3ml per patient split in 2 treatment sessions at a 4 months interval);
Juvederm Voluma: 20mg/ml, it is injected 5ml per patient per treatment (a total of 3ml per patient split in 2 treatment sessions at a 4 months interval)
